    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "どう思う？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you think?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_03-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "えー？　何が？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? About what?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.3583447217941282,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "見てたくせに。気配、あったぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on‚ you saw what happened. I sensed you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.802199649810791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 8.592063713073731
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_03-mna002.m4a",
      "text": "はは……バレてたか……\n結局、琴乃に聞かなかったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha. Oops‚ you caught me.\nSo‚ you didn’t end up saying anything to Kotono?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.925397046407063,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_03-mna003.m4a",
      "text": "ボーッとしてたけど\n何か悩みでもあるんじゃないのか？　……って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You spaced out for a while‚\nso I thought maybe you were agonizing over what to say.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.425397046407063,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 19.492063713073733
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "明日は本番だからね。琴乃が自分から話すなら\nともかく、俺の方から無理に聞き出すのもな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ tomorrow is the day. If Kotono brings it up herself‚ then that’s one thing‚\nbut it wouldn’t be right for me to force her to talk.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.59206371307374,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_03-mna004.m4a",
      "text": "あんなに様子がおかしいのに？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though she’s acting strange?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.758730379740403,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 27.758730379740445
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（麻奈の言う通り、琴乃の様子はおかしかった）\n（勝負が怖くなったのだろうか。それとも……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Mana is right. Kotono was acting strange.)\n(Is she scared of the competition? Or…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.25918391545614,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 39.059183915456174
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 39.39251724878947
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_03-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "…………私、どうして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tell me… why am I…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.359183915456136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 43.1746941884359
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（「どうして」……その先は分からない）\n（ただ、何か悩みがあるのは間違いない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(“Why am I”… I never heard the rest of her question.)\n(But it’s obvious that she’s worried about something.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.80802752176922,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 51.378027521769205
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 51.378027521769205
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "心当たりは？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Have any ideas?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.44136085510252,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 53.729909622669204
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_03-mna005.m4a",
      "text": "…………私？\nない……かな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Me?\nNot… really.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.46324295600256,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_03-mna006.m4a",
      "text": "でも、ついこの前までは\n元気だったんでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But until quite recently‚\nshe was doing well‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.26324295600257,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 62.7965762893359
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "まあね。本戦出場が決まったし、さくらともしっかり\n話し合ったし、みんなでパーティーもしてたしな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Since the competition order was settled‚ she and Sakura\ntalked it through‚ and everyone had a party‚ too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.6299096226692,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 71.39657628933588
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_03-mna007.m4a",
      "text": "今日のグランプリのステージを見て\n急に何か気になることが出来たとか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do you think watching the Grand Prix performance today\nsuddenly gave her something to worry about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.6965762893359,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ステージに立つリズノワとトリエルの凄さに\n自信をなくした、っていうのが一番ありそうだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Seeing LizNoir and TRINITYAiLE’s incredible performance on stage\nand losing confidence would be the most likely explanation‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.23689936760701,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_03-mna008.m4a",
      "text": "違うの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But you don’t think it’s that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.036899367607,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 84.036899367607
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、そうじゃない\n俺の勘だけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. I don’t.\nAt least‚ that’s what my gut tells me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.62490391297776,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_03-mna009.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ何？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ what is it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.29157057964443,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 89.29157057964443
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（やはり、直接聞いてみるしかないか……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I guess asking her directly is my only option after all.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.89667264186976,
